# Amber Alerts | Code For India | [Hackathon] 2015 
 [Hackathon]: <http://codeforindia.org/hackathon2015/>
#### Amber Alerts In Support of Digital India Vision

> To Enable law enforcement agencies to issue amber alerts for missing childrent and get them pushed to social media and mobile.
 


```sh
Features
1.Report a lost person, our website generates emails, sms, facebook post, twitter tweets to all the people which are within 5 km radius from the last seen location of that person.
2.We list the listing of all lost people, if somebody has found an unrecognised person, he may check his listing on our website and contact his family.
3.There are real time graphs, showing how many lost cases were solved
```

#### Technologies Used
````
- NodeJs
- MongoDB
- Materialise CSS
- D3.js
- JSON
- GMail, Twitter, Facebook, Twilio APIs
- HTML Canvas to generate posters
````

